        public java.lang.String getInfo​(java.lang.String identifier,
                                Cell cell)
        Gets meta data from cell
        Parameters:
        identifier - determines which part of the metadata to extract
        cell - the cell with the meta data
        Returns:
        if identifier is "name" return the name of the cell, otherwise return the animation frame (for syncing)
